        "content": "<p>Something that is happening to me with <code>Cslib.ReductionSystem</code> is that I want to use things that are defined for relations with it. I could redefine them for <code>Cslib.ReductionSystem</code>, but I don't think that is a nice solution. Do you have some suggestion of what to do?</p>",
